description: Raa is a fictional character appearing in Marvel Comics. He first appeared in Fantastic Four Annual #25 as a member of The Anachronauts (Apocryphus, Deathunt 9000, Ssith, Tyndar, Wildrun (aka Red Wolf), and Sir Raston). He was created by writer Mark Gruenwald and penciler Herb Trimpe.
name: Raa of the Caves
